3. FONTS:
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
Headings: Bebas Neue, Body: DM Sans

4. LAYOUT:
- html, body: margin:0; padding:0; background:#0a0a0f; color:#f0f0f0; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; overflow-x:hidden;
- Outer wrapper: max-width:1400px; margin:0 auto; padding:20px;
