6. KPI STRIP — only for full dashboard requests — single row of 5 equal cards, margin-bottom: 20px:
- Total Records, Avg Price, Top Make, Top Location, Top Fuel Type
- Card: background #12121a, border-radius 12px, padding 16px 20px
- Label: 11px uppercase letter-spacing 1px color #6b6b80
- Value: Bebas Neue 32px color #e8ff47
- Trend: font-size 12px, ▲ green #2ecc71, ▼ red #e74c3c
- CRITICAL: If a KPI value cannot be determined from the data, hide that card entirely — NEVER show "NOT CALCULATED", "N/A", or any placeholder text

7. MAIN GRID — 2 column, margin-bottom: 20px:
- grid-template-columns: 55% 45%; gap: 20px;
- Left: vertical bar chart card — Top 10 Makes by count
