  * Card title: "Top 10 Makes" 13px uppercase #6b6b80 margin-bottom 12px
  * Canvas wrapper: position:relative; height:320px; width:100%;
- Right: 2 doughnut chart cards stacked vertically
  * display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px;
  * Each doughnut card: background #12121a, border-radius 12px, padding 20px
  * Card title: 13px uppercase #6b6b80 margin-bottom 12px
  * Canvas wrapper: position:relative; height:200px; width:100%;

8. BOTTOM ROW — 2 columns, margin-bottom: 20px:
- grid-template-columns: 38% 62%; gap: 20px;
- Left: vertical bar chart — Top 10 Makes by count
  * Card: background #12121a, border-radius 12px, padding 20px
  * Card title: "Makes Distribution" 13px uppercase #6b6b80 margin-bottom 12px
  * Canvas wrapper: position:relative; height:320px; width:100%;
- Right: INDIA MAP card
